metadata.name: Pons X Little Man!
metadata.description: Cayden loves the The Plague Frogs, he also loves epic adventure tales! His little frog is one of his favorite NFTs in his whole collection! He decided to create a derivative of the one and only Pons, the fearless leader of The Plague Frogs! We are very excited to share this with all the frogs in the pond! üê∏üåàüíô
